This product bundles a synonym dictionary (sdsearch-core/src/synonyms.bin)
derived from the following third-party lexical resources:

- Princeton WordNet 3.0 (English). Licensed under the WordNet License:
  https://wordnet.princeton.edu/license-and-commercial-use

- Multilingual Central Repository (MCR), Spanish wordnet. Licensed under
  Creative Commons Attribution 3.0 (CC BY 3.0):
  https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/

Both are distributed via the Open Multilingual Wordnet (OMW) and linked through
the Collaborative Interlingual Index (CILI). The bundled dictionary is a
derivative work: lemmas grouped by shared interlingual synset, lowercased,
accent-folded on the lookup key, deduplicated and capped, for query-time
expansion. No search index data is affected.
